{"tid":1130317,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[5.1勞動節] 委內瑞拉史上最大規模示威 瓜伊多號召推翻馬杜洛","createTime":"2019-04-29T03:03:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-01T07:52:17.000Z","uid":141151,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c60d7671d3664523d19c00730bcb3486f7a33180","tid":1130317,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T03:03:21.000Z","msg":"委內瑞拉史上最大規模 瓜伊多號召推翻馬杜洛<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A7%94%E5%85%A7%E7%91%9E%E6%8B%89%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E8%A6%8F%E6%A8%A1-%E7%93%9C%E4%BC%8A%E5%A4%9A%E8%99%9F%E5%8F%AC%E6%8E%A8%E7%BF%BB%E9%A6%AC%E6%9D%9C%E6%B4%9B-005519546.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25A7%2594%25E5%2585%25A7%25E7%2591%259E%25E6%258B%2589%25E5%258F%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A6%258F%25E6%25A8%25A1-%25E7%2593%259C%25E4%25BC%258A%25E5%25A4%259A%25E8%2599%259F%25E5%258F%25AC%25E6%258E%25A8%25E7%25BF%25BB%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E6%259D%259C%25E6%25B4%259B-005519546.html&d=5ezJA%2FdytRM7iHrFGdkn9SMX%2BuEjOoKUanh%2Bi4Xf2cM%3D&h=ab2e0711\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A7%94%E5%85%A7%E7%91%9E%E6%8B%89%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E8%A6%8F%E6%A8%A1-%E7%93%9C%E4%BC%8A%E5%A4%9A%E8%99%9F%E5%8F%AC%E6%8E%A8%E7%BF%BB%E9%A6%AC%E6%9D%9C%E6%B4%9B-005519546.html</a><br />\n<br />\n委內瑞拉反對派領袖瓜伊多(Juan Guaido)27日再次呼籲軍方停止對委內瑞拉總統馬杜洛(Nicolas Maduro)政權的支持。他同時宣佈，將在勞動節舉行委內瑞拉史上最大規模示威，以推翻這位四面楚歌的總統。<br />\n<br />\n瓜伊多在首都卡拉卡斯(Caracas)的集會告訴群眾，軍方的支持是罷黜馬杜洛行動的「基石」，但時間在流逝，不可能永遠等待，他提醒軍方他們正肩負著一個歷史機會。<br />\n<br />\n瓜伊多是委內瑞拉國會議長，他在今年1月挑戰馬杜洛的合法性，自行宣佈為委內瑞拉臨時總統。儘管已獲得包括美國在內50多個國家承認，但由於馬杜洛有軍方支持，瓜伊多至今仍無法撼動馬杜洛的地位。<br />\n<br />\n瓜伊多將在5月1日舉行一場大規模的勞動節抗議活動，以維持對馬杜洛政權的街頭壓力。他表示，這將是「委內瑞拉史上規模最大的一次抗議活動」。<br />\n<br />\n在此同時，委內瑞拉政府也號召大規模的親馬杜洛示威，作為其年度勞動節遊行的一部份。<br />\n<br />\n有數千名馬杜洛的支持者27日湧上街頭，回應執政黨─委內瑞拉聯合社會黨(PSUV)的號召，「慶祝」委內瑞拉退出美洲國家組織(OAS)。<br />\n<br />\n委內瑞拉是在2017年宣佈將離開這個組織，並指責OAS參與一場由美國主導的破壞委內瑞拉政府穩定行動。<br />\n<br />\n馬杜洛在推特發文嘲諷說，核心人物正在動員起來，慶祝委內瑞拉撤出美國殖民地辦公室(US Colonial Office)：OAS。<br />\n<br />\n在OAS於10日表決同意，由瓜伊多的特使代表委內瑞拉，直到新的總統選出之後，馬杜洛的大使已經離開OAS。"},{"pid":"cabb51e330cdc704f27febe38bfd67f047ee02f8","tid":1130317,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T23:59:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e9d79f91c431d0a22f9b5beae6af0f424aa5c71","tid":1130317,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T00:44:20.000Z","msg":"然後軍政府執政<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66a352f93febb0d4c48b998d0d985ae20b823396","tid":1130317,"uid":11097,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T16:42:56.000Z","msg":"瓜：時間唔等人，依家唔做野實衰硬<br />\n<br />\n黃：大家千其唔好去旺角，唔好講咁多，起返首歌先，Music！⋯⋯⋯<br />\n今天我～～～<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21d2ddad0499d9bfc0d42daf96bbe5a102fbdf06","tid":1130317,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T02:24:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d23619326c1b886e94339edc98f4faa18558085","tid":1130317,"uid":166474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T02:25:31.000Z","msg":"馬杜羅係民選喎，推翻佢係咪唔尊重民主制度？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26ea293514006e032968d5c992cb5fd612874e36","tid":1130317,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T07:50:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9d3b99fd86f08b39e5fd6979b678a2f12891589","tid":1130317,"uid":37232,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T07:52:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JRcDYyy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/t